==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Screaming
<hw>Scream"ing</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Uttering screams;
shrieking.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having the nature of a scream; like a scream;
shrill; sharp.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The fearful matrons raise a <qex>screaming</qex> cry.</q>
<rj><qau>Dryden.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scree</ent>⟦br⟧
